System configuration:

	Linux (on all hardware platforms)

Latest Icon version:

	Version 9.4.1

Installer:

	Gregg Townsend
	Icon Project
	The University of Arizona

Missing features:

	None

Known bugs:

	On Intel Itanium with gcc v2.96, change "-O2" to "-O"
	in Makedefs after configuring.  This fixes errors seen
	in the "large" test of multiprecision integers.

Comments:

	Tested under Red Hat Linux versions 6.0 (Alpha), 
	7.1 (Intel x86, Itanium), and 7.2 (Intel x86).

	This configuration can use pthreads for context switching,
	and must use pthreads on the Intel Itanium.

Date:

	March 4, 2002
